34","canonical_id":"2607.14034","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Supermagnified Stars in Lensing Clusters and Small-Scale Structure in the Dark Matter","authors":["Gabriel Torralba","Jordi Miralda-Escudé"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO"],"summary":"本文提出超放大恒星（由HST和JWST在星系团透镜中发现）因星系团内恒星产生的微透镜事件，可用于探测暗物质小尺度结构，并借助HWO望远镜实现独特的高分辨率观测。","date":"2026-07-16","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.14034","score":57,"stars":3,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Other Selected Research"]}],"must_read":[]}